{"id": 2313, "genre": 1001, "title": "你的“工作后压力”都来自哪儿？", "description": "下班回家就轻松了？不，其实只有（加班错过晚高峰）的路上那不到一个小时可以算得上轻松吧。（题图来自：iStock©sorbetto）", "record_count": 2869, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180502170444PsCnSEuKF5mqRYdW.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-05-15T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 282113, "content": "无所事事，没有干劲", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1246938}, {"id": 282114, "content": "不知道在忙啥\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 818716}, {"id": 282115, "content": "加班，私人生活被牺牲掉的烦躁", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346065}, {"id": 282371, "content": "人际关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1342772}, {"id": 282117, "content": "做完一大堆无意义地工作之后已经没有精力去做真正能提高自己的事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346075}, {"id": 282629, "content": "24*7小时微信工作群，听见滴滴声就紧张", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1335121}, {"id": 282118, "content": "工作之后的空余时间用来学习，感觉总是不能很用心", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346073}, {"id": 285959, "content": "穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366390}, {"id": 282120, "content": "明明就只需要专注工作还要专注活跃公司群气氛", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 749624}, {"id": 282376, "content": "处女座发现自己有事情是做的不完美，不让人满意的时候压力就很大。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1347256}, {"id": 282632, "content": "来自于忙了一天忙得却和理想无关仅仅用来解决温饱的事，然而它消磨了我的时间让我无暇顾及我的梦想", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1348470}, {"id": 282121, "content": "工作量大到已经快没有睡觉时间了，一大堆属于工作且不被领导认可的事情烦杂不堪！更别谈周末了，感觉生活已经被工作侵略的所剩无几了\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346083}, {"id": 282122, "content": "没目标 日复一日 想着有进步 但是不知道朝哪个方向努力", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346085}, {"id": 282123, "content": "每天都忙着，但是找不到前进的方向了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1294103}, {"id": 282124, "content": "大多数时候，消耗你能量的不只是事，而是遇到的人。干活本身是不累的，平衡情绪最累。", "image": "img/option/option/20180516085036irZUX97o0kABsEYf", "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1342943}, {"id": 282127, "content": "每天都要做同样的事，没有新鲜感", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1335135}, {"id": 283919, "content": "被催婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1356661}, {"id": 282129, "content": "只能创造老板满足感而不能实现自我认同价值的加班是可耻的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666852}, {"id": 282130, "content": "忙忙碌碌，才不觉得忙", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1294328}, {"id": 282133, "content": "假期微信能不能安静一下。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346141}, {"id": 283670, "content": "1、感受到没有发展空间；\r\n2、感觉公司给钱不到位；\r\n3、放工没人约；\r\n4、临下班安排工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1136135}, {"id": 282135, "content": "钱少事多心里负担重。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346129}, {"id": 282136, "content": "只有开车在路上才有时间听听歌，思考下近期的得失。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1168893}, {"id": 282137, "content": "干了自己最不适合干的工作，确要为了生存一直坚守着，天天烦事一大堆，每天心提着，好迷茫，无奈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1343746}, {"id": 282138, "content": "对于甲方爸爸的无理要求，领导永远都是辛苦一下，加加班吧，事后可以倒休，可是总是永无止境的加班", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 791738}, {"id": 282139, "content": "永远不知道领导在微信群转发什么文章让你必须看，隔天讨论", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198027}, {"id": 282140, "content": "没能力，没背景，没依靠，看不到未来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346174}, {"id": 282144, "content": "觉得自己在很积极努力的生活，其实是一个积极废人，假装很努力", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346196}, {"id": 282145, "content": "领导猪头一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 500778}, {"id": 281891, "content": "和不同层次同事的相处", "image": null, "praise_count": 72, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1248992}, {"id": 282147, "content": "心理负担大，回家以后还有一些收尾工作，电话随时都在想", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1343069}, {"id": 281892, "content": "来自觉得忙碌不堪却没有变强", "image": null, "praise_count": 694, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 721151}, {"id": 281893, "content": "要写工作总结", "image": null, "praise_count": 73, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1060674}, {"id": 281897, "content": "与人相处很复杂。想法意见从不被采纳。越来越没有工作的激情", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1345327}, {"id": 281898, "content": "日复一日 月复一月 年复一年", "image": null, "praise_count": 114, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725485}, {"id": 281899, "content": "加班以后工作日调休的时候，工作的电话一个接一个，放假就是换个地方工作。", "image": null, "praise_count": 135, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 720819}, {"id": 281900, "content": "业绩指标", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 980503}, {"id": 282156, "content": "怎么没有sb领导这个选项呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 790396}, {"id": 281901, "content": "认知自我和自我反思~", "image": "img/option/option/20180515112942F0cr5mJqiaKevSUn.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 716017}, {"id": 283949, "content": "没背景 没能力 没依靠", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1237001}, {"id": 281902, "content": "日复一日做一样的事情，量变却不能引起质变", "image": null, "praise_count": 52, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1009956}, {"id": 281903, "content": "天天忙碌的工作，却找不到自我价值的认同，工资也是低的可怜。", "image": null, "praise_count": 427, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1128485}, {"id": 282159, "content": "投入的时间精力换不回等价的回报", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1339329}, {"id": 281904, "content": "平淡的感觉。勾心斗角。大部分时间都在重复着简单且无趣的事情。节奏很快的单休。一遍又一遍的重复的工作日。", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1205194}, {"id": 281905, "content": "前景的不确定性", "image": null, "praise_count": 107, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 306892}, {"id": 281906, "content": "没什么事干，找不到目标，很迷茫，不算压力", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1345308}, {"id": 281907, "content": "人人都为前途奔忙", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340372}, {"id": 282164, "content": "太依赖于现状", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346315}, {"id": 281909, "content": "微信QQ消息不停又不敢直接下线", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 971662}, {"id": 283701, "content": "工作四年后，有次去看事业单位，结果发现连作文都不会写了，why?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1351741}]}